targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias(date_time_date,1s),
  demand AS metric,
  delay,
  loss
FROM flowcharting
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(date_time_date)
GROUP BY 1,2
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(date_time_date,1s)

SELECT
  srcIP AS "源节点(0-99)",
  dstIP AS "目的节点(0-99)",
  flow AS "流量/kB"
FROM traffic
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(date_time_date)
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(date_time_date,1s)
